      <div xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159">
        <head xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Hd1e99" type="question-title">De continentia visus</head>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e102">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e112" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e104">Gregorius, in
              <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e112">Ne quaedam lubrica in cogitatione versemus,
              providendum nobis est, quod intueri non decet, quod non licet concupisci.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e117">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e127" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e119">Gregorius, in
              <title>Moralibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e127">Sancti viri, cum sinistra pulsari delectatione
              se sentiunt, ipsa, per quae formae species ad mentem ingrediuntur, disciplinae
              magisterio lumina restringunt, ne pravae cogitationi visio lenocinata
              famuletur.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e132">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e142" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e134">Augustinus, in
              <title>Regula</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e142">Oculi vestri, etsi jactantur in aliquam
              feminarum, in nulla figantur. Neque enim, quando proceditis, feminas videre
              prohibemini; sed appetere, vel ab ipsis appeti velle, criminosum est.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e147">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e157" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e149">Augustinus,
              <title>de Confessionibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e157" source="http://scta.info/resource/aconf-l10-d1e356">
              Resisto seductionibus oculorum meorum, ne
              implicentur pedes affectus mei, quibus ingredior viam tuam, Deus meus; et erigo ad te
              invisibiles oculos meos, ut tu evellas de laqueo pedes meos.
            </quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e163">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e173" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e165">Augustinus,
              <title>de Poenitentia</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e173">Cohibeat se a ludis, a spectaculis saeculi, qui
              perfectam vult consequi gratiam remissionis. Nam Dina si se cohibuisset, si inter suos
              remansisset, ab extraneo raptore corrupta non fuisset.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e178">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e188" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e180">Isidorus, in
              <title>Synonymis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e188">Tolle occasionem peccandi, aufer materiam
              delinquendi: si vis esse a fornicatione tutus, esto corpore et visione
              discretus.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e193">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e203" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e195">Isidorus, in
              <title>Synonymis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e203">Peccati pudore oculos tuos attollere erubesce.
              Incede abjecto vultu, humiliato ore, deposita facie.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e208">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e218" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e210">Ambrosius,
              <title>de Officiis</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e218">Est in oculis verecundia, ut nес videre viros
              femina pudica, nес videri velit.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e223">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e233" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e225">Ambrosius,
              <title>super Lucam</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e233">Quod non videris, non amabis; sed ubi caro
              concupierit, compatientis quoque animi constantia defatiscit, et mens consortio amoris
              inflectitur.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e238">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e248" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e240">Bernardus, in
              <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e248">Ut te ipsum semper aspicias, ab omnibus oculos
              averte.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e254">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e264" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e256">Bernardus,
              <title>de duodecim Gradibus</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e264">Utquid audes oculos levare ad coelum, qui
              peccasti in coelum? Terram intuere, ut cognoscas teipsum: ipsa te tibi repraesentabit,
              quia terra es, et in terram ibis. Duabus tamen causis inculpabiliter oculos levas, ut
              petas auxilium a Deo, vel impendas proximo.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
        <p xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-d1e269">
          <ref corresp="#UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e279" xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Rd1e271">Seneca, in
              <title>Epistola</title>
          </ref>
          <cit>
            <quote xml:id="UUyf3f-d1e24159-Qd1e279">Qui deponere vult desideria rerum omnium, quarum
              cupiditate flagraverit, et oculos, et aures ab his, quae relinquit, avertat.</quote>
          </cit>
        </p>
      </div>
